<i>♪ Babatiin kita ♪</i>

28
00:01:58.133 --> 00:02:00.300
<i>♪ Binabati kita sa iyong pagbubuntis ♪</i>

29
00:02:00.300 --> 00:02:02.900
Binabati kita, Manager Jang.

30
00:02:03.733 --> 00:02:05.756
Binabati kita.

31
00:02:05.756 --> 00:02:07.367
<i>♪Ha♪</i>

32
00:02:07.367 --> 00:02:11.700
<i>♪ Nararapat kang batiin ♪</i>

33
